name: Jonathan Sahagun
text: .  Du30 Fans: May free speech kami! We have the right to be toxic online! DAVAO! DAVAO! DAVAO!    Me: Putangina. Pag martial law na tingnan natin kung saan ka dadalhin ng free speech na yan.
